{"tid":2223343,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"12港人送中︱鄧棨然無歸期 中秋不能與家人團圓 胞弟感慨：月亮好似少咗一忽","createTime":"2020-09-29T17:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T05:44:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e3cc4b9f53b9669fff3c2ab7525c24df99ccb119","tid":2223343,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:55:41.000Z","msg":"中秋佳節本應人月兩團圓，12名在中國被扣押港青的家屬卻與至親相隔兩地，更加無法得知家人的消息。被捕人之一鄧棨然胞弟感慨，一家四口歷年無論如何忙碌，中秋節都會抽時間做節團圓，今年飯桌只剩自己和兩老，凝望哥哥往日常坐位置，他難掩悲痛：「月亮好似少咗一忽，中秋唔再係人月團圓。」藉着中秋，鄧弟向林鄭班子喊話，要求高官反思，若自己有家人在不知情下被捉走，會否同樣覺得，事不關己？<br />\n<br />\n而在被捕者未能獲享應有的法律保障、港府又冷待之時，左派更肆意抹黑，如前特首梁振英撰文說12人涉反修例案件並非「善男信女」。鄧棨然胞弟接受《蘋果》電話專訪時反駁，指年長他3年的哥哥為人善良文靜，平日只愛好行山和彈結他，絕對算得上是上進好青年，透露哥哥大學畢業後即努力工作儲蓄，5年前開始玩具模型網購生意，白手興家創業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/RCSR3XOP6NBSDJCNMV37Q3QBI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FRCSR3XOP6NBSDJCNMV37Q3QBI4%2F&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWPsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=aaca2647\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FRCSR3XOP6NBSDJCNMV37Q3QBI4%2F&h=f696eccf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/RCSR3XOP6NBSDJCNMV37Q3QBI4/</a>"},{"pid":"d2c3769f5e7f66ebcd17ae39fa181f10f3d5acc0","tid":2223343,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27da41ce5ed0ff33595142989a659ccc104aa7e3","tid":2223343,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2c3769f5e7f66ebcd17ae39fa181f10f3d5acc0","tid":2223343,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T17:56:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/